SYNOPSIS
========
   #include <sys/driver_hooks.h>
   set_driver_hook(H_NO_IPC_SLOT, value)

DESCRIPTION
===========
   Arguments:
      - **value** (*int*) -- 0
      - **value** (*string*) -- <msg>

   Optional hook specifying the message given to logins rejected due to space
   limitations (MAX_PLAYER). Hook setting has to be string.

   If set to 0, the default message "Lpmud is full. Come back later." is
   issued.

SEE ALSO
========
   *hooks*
